we can provide training and support if needed.<br>If we don't have any volunteer then the list will be closed on Friday 5th September 2014.<br>When this happens subscribers will not be able to post messages to the list but archives will [...]   </description>   <dc:date>2014-08-20T16:00:21+01:00</dc:date>   <dc:creator>JiscMail Helpline</dc:creator>   <dc:identifier>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BUSINESSOBJECTS;7ca7e44d.1408</dc:identifier> </item>  <item rdf:about="https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BUSINESSOBJECTS;847e1442.1407">   <title>New list owner required for BUSINESSOBJECTS JiscMail list </title>   <link>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BUSINESSOBJECTS;847e1442.1407</link>   <description> JiscMail Helpline has recently tried to contact the list owners of this list, but the message we sent bounced.<br><br>In order for us to continue to provide this mailing list we require an existing subscriber(s) from a UK Educational/Research Organisation to volunteer to take over the running of the list. JiscMail Helpline is currently managing the list as a temporary measure, if you wish to volunteer to run this list - check that you meet the criteria for running a list: https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk/groups/startagroup/grouprequestform.html and if you do contact helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk as soon as you possibly can. [...]   </description>   <dc:date>2014-07-29T16:42:53+01:00</dc:date>   <dc:creator>JiscMail Helpline</dc:creator>   <dc:identifier>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=BUSINESSOBJECTS;847e1442.1407</dc:identifier> </item>   </rdf:RDF>
